            <description><![CDATA[【“用我的皮！”女儿严重烫伤，爸爸一句话让人直接泪奔<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[苦涩]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/7e/2021_bitter_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】手皮脚皮脱落、休克、发烧...女孩在家不慎被开水大面积烫伤，爸爸抱着她火速赶到医院，陷入深深自责。当医生提出后续治疗的最佳方案是植皮时，爸爸想都没想：“妹妹还小，用我的皮给她补回来。” 医生摇摇头：“不行，得用她自己的皮。” 由于没有买医保，手术费让爸爸当场犯了难，但他一心想办法筹钱，给女儿做康复治疗。（拍摄已签署授权书） <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4907415951573075" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hehe5d13lhj21hc0u0q52.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/REVY8SEWgx085RG4tzQA01041201dQZe0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685524772&amp;ssig=GIK%2BfF%2B43s&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/5kK4uQQFgx085RG3Fbpu01041200EnXk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685524772&amp;ssig=gVzEjQR9WY&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/qlBMoR04gx085RG39ttS01041200pYZ00E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685524772&amp;ssig=ldjjk4wE5m&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4907415951573075&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" targe